ty_two_week_low":99.9,"fifty_day_average":128.653,"two_hundred_day_avg":142.0515,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":178.0,"all_time_low":99.9,"long_business_summary":"Kings Infra Ventures Limited operates as an aquaculture company in India and internationally. It operates through Infrastructure and Aquaculture segments. The company engages in aquaculture and shrimp contract farming; seafood processing; trading in marine products; aquaculture consultancy; retail of frozen seafood products under the Kings Frigo brand and ready-to-eat seafood-based meals and snacks under the Kings Bento brand; and land banking activities. It also provides aqua health care products, including micro and macro minerals, feed supplementary, water and soil probiotics, immunostimulants, ammonia reducers, nitrate and nitrite reducers, white gut, white mussel heelers, vitamins, herbal growth promoters, herbal vibrio controllers, and natural binders under the Aqua Kings brand. In addition, the company develops aquaculture and seafood production infrastructure, as well as infrastructure for integrated life spaces, logistics, warehousing, hospitality, healthcare, education, and clean energy. It exports its products to China, Europe, South Korea, Vietnam, and the Middle East. The company was formerly known as Victory Aqua Farm Ltd. and changed its name to Kings Infra Ventures Limited in April 2007. Kings Infra Ventures Limited was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Kochi, India."}}